# Marketplace Publishing

Before any marketplace upload, run this first:

```bash
claude plugin validate .
```

If that passes, most issues are covered. Consult this skill for gotchas the validator does not catch and for schema reference.

## Minimum valid marketplace.json

```json
{
  "name": "my-team-plugins",
  "owner": { "name": "My Team", "email": "ops@example.com" },
  "plugins": [
    { "name": "my-plugin", "source": ".", "description": "Team workflow plugin" }
  ]
}
```

