## The 4 gotchas (one-liners — details in references/gotchas.md)

1. Never start name with `claude-`, `anthropic-`, or `official-` — these prefixes are reserved.
2. Version in `marketplace.json` is silently overridden by `plugin.json` version.
3. Relative paths (`./foo`) only work with git-based marketplaces, not URL-based.
4. kebab-case is mandatory for Claude.ai sync — the local validator only warns.
